# Peggy UI — Material UI

UI stack is MUI only — never add Tailwind.

- Theme: `theme/peggyTheme.ts` (`eyebrowSx`, `monoSx`, `cardHoverSx`).
- Shell: `AppShell`, `DashboardPage`, `ResearcherProfile`.
- Nav: Dashboard, **Corpus** (literature), **Our findings**, **Ask Peggy**, Gap Analysis, Comparison.
- Corpus: `CorpusManagement` — literature only; **Add literature** modal (`IngestModal`).
- Our findings: `/findings` — `FindingsManagement` + **Add our findings** modal (`FindingsModal`).
- Pages: `PageHeader` + MUI `Paper`.
- Fonts: Inter + JetBrains Mono via `next/font` in `app/layout.tsx`.

## Demo vs live data

When corpus is empty, use demo placeholder stats (142 papers, 94% indexed) and the demo activity feed.

When corpus has data, show live API data.

Workspace copy: `NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKSPACE_TITLE`, `NEXT_PUBLIC_WORKSPACE_FOCUS` in `apps/web/.env.local`.
